import React from 'react';
import Container from '../../common/Container/Container';
import Link from '../../common/Link/Link';
import Typography from '../../common/Typography/Typography';
import { FontAwesomeIcon } from '@fortawesome/react-fontawesome';
import {
  faFacebook,
  faInstagram,
  faTwitter,
} from '@fortawesome/free-brands-svg-icons';
import {
  faEnvelope,
  faPhone,
  faMapMarkedAlt,
} from '@fortawesome/free-solid-svg-icons';
import { footer } from '../../content/footer';
import './Footer.scss';

const Footer = () => (
  <Container customClass="footer">
    <Container customClass="footer__container">
      <Typography variant="h3" customClass="footer__title">
        ABOUT US
      </Typography>
      <Typography variant="p" customClass="footer__description">
        Far far away, behind the word mountains, far from the countries Vokalia
        and Consonantia, there live the blind texts.
      </Typography>
      <Container customClass="footer__socials">
        <Link link="/">
          <FontAwesomeIcon icon={faFacebook} />
        </Link>
        <Link link="/">
          <FontAwesomeIcon icon={faTwitter} />
        </Link>
        <Link link="/">
          <FontAwesomeIcon icon={faInstagram} />
        </Link>
      </Container>
    </Container>
    <Container customClass="footer__container">
      <Typography variant="h3" customClass="footer__title">
        HAVE A QUESTIONS?
      </Typography>
      <Container customClass="footer__info">
        <Container customClass="footer__details">
          <FontAwesomeIcon icon={faMapMarkedAlt} />
          <Typography variant="p" customClass="footer__description">
            203 Fake St. Mountain View, San Francisco, California, USA
          </Typography>
        </Container>
        <Container customClass="footer__details">
          <FontAwesomeIcon icon={faPhone} />
          <Typography variant="p" customClass="footer__description">
            +2 392 3929 210
          </Typography>
        </Container>
        <Container customClass="footer__details">
          <FontAwesomeIcon icon={faEnvelope} />
          <Typography variant="p" customClass="footer__description">
            info@yourdomain.com
          </Typography>
        </Container>
      </Container>
    </Container>
  </Container>
);

export default Footer;
